# termux_root
Hi; This repository is for downloading the rooted version of Termux and granting sudo access without the need to root your phone.
# termux_root

## Requirements

- Termux
- Python 3
- Git

## Installation

bash
pkg update && pkg upgrade -y
pkg install git python -y
git clone https://github.com/BLACKtoov/termux_root.git
cd termux_root
python termux_root.py


## Usage

After running the command above, the script will start automatically.

